#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:2
msgid "Tighten a carbon cap"
msgstr "收紧碳排放上限"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:4
msgid ""
"**Goal.** Run a counterfactual with a stricter system-wide CO2 cap "
"without overwriting the baseline."
msgstr "**目标。** 在不覆盖基线的前提下,运行一个更严格的系统级 CO2 上限的反事实情景。"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:7
msgid ""
"PREP-SHOT registers a CLI flag for every input file in ``params.json``. "
"Pass ``--<param>=<suffix>`` and PREP-SHOT loads ``<file>_<suffix>.csv`` "
"instead of ``<file>.csv``. Output names get the same suffix."
msgstr ""
"PREP-SHOT 为 ``params.json`` 中的每个输入文件注册了命令行参数。传入 ``--<param>=<suffix"
">``,PREP-SHOT 会加载 ``<file>_<suffix>.csv`` 而非 "
"``<file>.csv``。输出文件名也会带上同样的后缀。"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:13
msgid "Steps"
msgstr "步骤"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:15
msgid ""
"**1. Copy the baseline policy file as a new variant.** From inside "
"``examples/<scenario>/input/``:"
msgstr "**1. 将基线策略文件复制为新变体。** 进入 ``examples/<scenario>/input/`` 后执行:"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:23
#, python-format
msgid ""
"**2. Edit the new file's 2030 cap.** The schema is ``(limit_id, year, "
"unit, value, zones)``. Open in your editor and change the cap from "
"``146000000`` (baseline) to ``80000000`` (about 55% of baseline):"
msgstr ""
"**2. 编辑新文件中 2030 年的上限。** 表格结构为 ``(limit_id, year, unit, value, "
"zones)``。在编辑器中打开,把上限从 ``146000000`` (基线) 改为 ``80000000`` (约为基线的 55%):"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:34
msgid "**3. Re-run with the variant flag.**"
msgstr "**3. 使用变体参数重新运行。**"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:41
msgid ""
"Output goes to ``output/baseline_tight.nc`` (or whatever your "
"``output_filename`` is, with ``_tight`` appended)."
msgstr ""
"结果输出至 ``output/baseline_tight.nc`` (或你定义的 ``output_filename`` 加上 "
"``_tight``)。"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:45
msgid "Verify"
msgstr "验证"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:47
msgid "Compare baseline vs tight by total cost and by 2030 emissions:"
msgstr "通过总成本和 2030 年排放量比较基线与收紧情景:"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:60
msgid ""
"The tight cap forces the model to either build more zero-carbon capacity,"
" dispatch existing zero-carbon capacity harder, or import clean power "
"from neighboring zones -- whichever is cheapest."
msgstr "更严格的上限迫使模型要么建设更多零碳容量,要么更高强度地调度已有零碳容量,要么从邻近区域进口清洁电力—— 三者中选最便宜的一项。"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:65
msgid "Custom cap regions"
msgstr "自定义上限区域"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:67
msgid ""
"The ``zones`` column accepts any comma-separated subset. For a Vietnam-"
"only cap:"
msgstr "``zones`` 列可以接受任意以逗号分隔的子集。例如仅针对越南的上限:"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:75
msgid ""
"Multiple ``limit_id`` rows for the same year stack as additional "
"constraints."
msgstr "同一年内多行 ``limit_id`` 会叠加为附加约束。"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:79
msgid "Common pitfalls"
msgstr "常见陷阱"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:81
msgid ""
"**Quote the zones string.** A comma inside an unquoted CSV cell splits "
"the column. Always wrap multi-zone lists in double quotes."
msgstr "**给 zones 字符串加引号。** 未加引号的 CSV 单元中的逗号会被当作列分隔符。多区域列表务必用双引号包裹。"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:83
msgid ""
"**The CLI suffix must be a valid filename suffix.** "
"``--carbon_emission_limit=tight`` looks for "
"``policy_carbon_emission_limit_tight.csv``, NOT "
"``policy_carbon_emission_limit-tight.csv``."
msgstr ""
"**CLI 后缀必须是合法的文件名后缀。** ``--carbon_emission_limit=tight`` 会查找 "
"``policy_carbon_emission_limit_tight.csv``,而非 "
"``policy_carbon_emission_limit-tight.csv``。"

#: ../../source/how_to/tighten_a_carbon_cap.rst:87
msgid ""
"**All cap regions must use existing zone names.** A typo silently "
"produces a constraint that's vacuously satisfied (no zones contribute), "
"giving you the wrong answer rather than an error. Double-check zone "
"spelling against ``demand.csv``."
msgstr ""
"**所有上限区域必须使用已有的区域名。** 拼写错误会静默生成一个无约束意义的条件 (没有区域贡献),给出错误答案而非报错。请对照 "
"``demand.csv`` 仔细核对区域拼写。"

